7.01	Helen_Crump	Helen Crump	Helen Crump is a fictional dramatic character on the American television program The Andy Griffith Show (1960-1968). Helen made her debut in the third season episode "Andy Discovers America" (1963). Helen was a schoolteacher and became main character Sheriff Andy Taylor's girlfriend. Helen also appeared in TAGS spinoff, Mayberry R.F.D. (1968 â€“ 1971), and in the TAGS reunion telemovie, Return to Mayberry (1986). Helen was portrayed by Aneta Corsaut.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Helen_01.JPG/200px-Helen_01.JPG
